{"tid":464421,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"搭巴士永遠冇後生女坐我隔離","createTime":"2017-11-10T13:34:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-10T19:23:17.000Z","uid":9531,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4066d6052adcaddb062997dd363a3ef281dbd1b5","tid":464421,"uid":9531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:34:33.000Z","msg":"U grad 咗一年，平時放工我都會搭巴士返屋企，而我搭嘅巴士通常都會坐滿，但每次坐我隔離永遠都唔會有後生女，而啲女如果冇得同番女坐，佢地多數同啲中年男人坐，甚至寧願同阿叔坐，但明明我隔離仲係未有人坐<br />\n自問冇體味，非油頭暗瘡IT毒撚樣，非肥胖人士，平時著老西，冇乜行李，冇坐過龍，究竟我邊度出咗問題？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實唔止搭巴士，係公司走廊行過遇到啲後生女同事，佢地連望都唔會望下我，而我就好似透明咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇人可以解答下我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：拍過兩次拖"},{"pid":"a070c79362ab71134de0d6090f3f88dbba7f5acb","tid":464421,"uid":54576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:36:42.000Z","msg":"畀張相嚟睇睇先"},{"pid":"eaf883244693aabfffc7bc966e4da3962dbd9982","tid":464421,"uid":76063,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:37:43.000Z","msg":"搭程巴士都要介意呢D野 你肯定有視姦D女啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3dcdd552841a2658c2b2345db4b515b4f9eb72e","tid":464421,"uid":33439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:39:26.000Z","msg":"因為唔想比你FF咁多"},{"pid":"24617e8684d24ad0116869509e524572982ab301","tid":464421,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:41:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>畀張相嚟睇睇先</blockquote>"},{"pid":"5f0d7d7a45e32480d8276392a1410473d894dec6","tid":464421,"uid":9531,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-10T13:42:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搭程巴士都要介意呢D野 你肯定有視姦D女啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n得閒望兩眼周圍姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c05e5777bacf3c7